 的完整曲目列表尚未公布。然而，这位艺术家分享了一段新音乐——请在此处观看“Gum”视频： </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="胶" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/VLf6w0L4HAM?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> Abstract 在最近的演出中，他预览了未发行的歌曲“Turn Me On”、“Running Out”、“What Should I Do”、“P（Intermission）”、“Voyager”、“Scream”、“Today I Gave Up”、 《Real 2 Me》和《麦当娜》。</p><p>自从《Arizona Baby》之后，这位明星分享了独立单曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brockhampton-kevin-abstract-slowthai-new-song-slugger-listen-2995192">《Slugger》</a> （与 $Not 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/slowthai">Slowthai</a>合作）和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kevin-abstract-shares-sierra-nights-video-featuring-ryan-beatty-3023417">《Sierra Nights》</a> （与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ryan-beatty">Ryan Beatty</a>合作）。</p><p>此外，去年<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/easy-life-share-new-kevin-abstract-collaboration-dear-miss-holloway-3233716">Abstract 与 Easy Life 合作制作了歌曲“Dear Miss Holloway”，</a>然后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2022-easy-life-kevin-abstract-interview-3255896">在 2022 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节上与乐队一起登台</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-brockhampton-play-their-final-concert-at-las-fonda-theatre-3352191">布罗克汉普顿 (Brockhampton) 去年 11 月在洛杉矶举行了最后一场演出，</a>此前他们放弃了最后一张专辑 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/brockhampton-the-family-review-kevin-abstract-3351690">《The Family》</a>和《TM》， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brockhampton-farewell-fans-with-new-album-tm-announce-live-streamed-final-performance-3351528">后者在没有任何事先声明的情况下就已发布</a>。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kevin-abstract-announces-fourth-solo-album-blanket-preorder-3513679">Kevin Abstract 宣布第四张个人专辑《Blanket》的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
