content/uploads/2023/10/DrakeGrammys-consideration-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/DrakeGrammys-consideration-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/drake">德雷克（Drake）</a>在扣留了他之前的两张唱片后，提交了他与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/21-savage">21 Savage</a>的合作专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/drake-and-21-savage-her-loss-review-3344009">《Her Loss》</a> ，以供<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/grammys">格莱美</a>考虑。</p><p>这位总共获得五项格莱美奖的加拿大艺术家近年来缺席了年度颁奖典礼，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/drake-grammys-2021-instagram-2825341">批评了唱片学院的提名程序</a>。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/drake-and-21-savage-her-loss-review-3344009">Drake 和 21 Savage – &#39;Her Loss&#39; 评论：令人兴奋的前景因懒惰的歌曲创作而受到损害</a></strong></li></ul><p>2021 年，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/drake-has-withdrawn-his-2022-grammy-nominations-3112349">德雷克在获得 2022 年格莱美奖两个类别的提名后退出了考虑</a>：最佳说唱专辑（ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/drake-certified-lover-boy-review-a-boring-bloated-disappointment-3036701">“Certified Lover Boy”</a> ）和最佳说唱表演（“Way 2 sexy”壮举<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/future">。Future</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/young-thug">Young Thug</a> ）。</p><p>然后，他决定不向今年的格莱美奖提交他的下一张个人专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/drake-honestly-nevermind-album-review-3250025">“Honestly, Nevermind”</a>或其任何单曲。</p><p>现在，据<a href="https://pitchfork.com/news/drake-ends-grammys-snub-submits-her-loss-for-consideration/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Pitchfork</em></a>报道，德雷克似乎结束了对颁奖典礼的抵制，将《她的损失》提交给<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/grammys-2024-to-add-three-new-awards-categories-including-best-african-music-performance-3455936">2024 年格莱美颁奖典礼</a>审议。这张联合唱片于 2022 年 11 月发行，已被提名为年度专辑和最佳说唱专辑。</p><p>此外，Drake 和 21 Savage 还提交了单曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/drake-21-savage-her-loss-album-cover-tracklist-3342646">“Rich Flex”</a>和“Spin Bout U”，以供五个不同类别的考虑：年度唱片、年度歌曲、最佳说唱表演、最佳说唱歌曲和最佳旋律说唱表演。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Drake, 21 Savage - Rich Flex（音频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/I4DjHHVHWAE?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> Drake 与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/travis-scott">Travis Scott</a> （ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/drake-takes-aim-at-pusha-t-and-pharrell-on-travis-scotts-meltdown-collab-3474998">《Meltdown》</a> ）和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/young-thug">Young Thug</a> （《Oh U Went》）在 2023 年合作的曲目也已提交。</p><p>明年的格莱美颁奖典礼将于 2 月 4 日在加利福尼亚州洛杉矶的 Crypto.com Arena 举行。提名将于11月10日公布，目前第一轮投票正在进行中。</p><p>早在 2020 年，Drake 就在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-weeknd">The Weeknd 的</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-weeknd-after-hours-review-his-most-all-encompassing-record-to-date-is-also-an-existential-quandary-2632591">《After Hours》</a>未获得任何提名后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/drake-grammys-2021-instagram-2825341">对格莱美进行了猛烈抨击</a>。</p><p>这位说唱歌手当时表示，他认为“我们不应该让自己每年都因为有影响力的音乐与这些奖项之间的脱节而感到震惊”。</p><p>他继续说道：“有一天，我说《The Weeknd》锁定了年度专辑或年度歌曲，还有无数其他合理的假设，但事实从来没有如此。”</p><p> Drake released his eighth and latest solo album, <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/drake-for-all-the-dogs-review-tracklist-lyrics-3511670">&#39;For All The Dogs&#39;</a> , last Friday (October 6).</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/drake-announces-break-from-music-to-focus-on-his-health-3510876">He has since announced that he will be taking a break from making music</a> , saying that he needs to prioritise his health.</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/drake-ends-grammys-boycott-by-submitting-her-loss-for-consideration-3513640">Drake ends Grammys boycott by submitting &#39;Her Loss&#39; for consideration</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> 